1. *Daleko* se vidi planina. (The mountain is visible far away.)
2. Živim *daleko* od grada. (I live far away from the city.)
3. Moja porodica je *daleko*. (My family is far away.)
4. *Daleko* je mesto gde živim. (The place where I live is far away.)
5. On je putovao *daleko*. (He traveled far away.)
6. *Daleke* zemlje su nam dostupne. (Far away countries are accessible to us.)
7. Moja deca putuju *daleko*. (My children are traveling far away.)
8. Ona ide *daleko*. (She is going far away.)